videos.description: TCU's Allen Robinson drives right baseline and scores on a reverse lay-in.
videos.headline: Robinson drives and finishes nifty lay-in for TCU

videos.description: Devonte' Graham leaves the game with apparent leg injury. Graham would later return to the game.
videos.headline: Devonte' Graham leaves the game with apparent leg injury

videos.description: Kansas's Dwight Coleby spins then scores in the paint.
videos.headline: Nice post move sets up Coleby to score for Kansas

videos.description: TCU's Alex Robinson  hits a three from the left wing to tie the game late in the first half.
videos.headline: Robinson buries 3-pointer to tie game

videos.description: TCU head coach Jamie Dixon on what allowed his team to have success in the first half.
videos.headline: Dixon: "We've got some confidence going right now"

videos.description: Kansas head coach Bill Self on what his team needs to do to hold of TCU in the second half.
videos.headline: Self: "We got our hands full this half"

videos.description: TCU's Kenrich Williams gives to Desmond Bane who cuts into the lane and finishes an easy lay-in.
videos.headline: TCU extends lead on Kansas

videos.description: Kansas's Frank Mason III drills a triple from the top of the key and draws a foul for a possible 4 point play.
videos.headline: Mason III drills 3-pointer and draws a foul

videos.description: On the break, Frank Mason III pulls up and connects on a 3-pointer to cut into the deficit against TCU.
videos.headline: Mason III pulls up and connects on huge 3-pointer

videos.description: TCU's Kenrich Williams tips in a missed shot and draws the foul on Kansas.
videos.headline: TCU scores on tip in late in second half

videos.description: Kansas' Frank Mason attacks the paint then hits a floater late in the second half.
videos.headline: Mason III hits crucial floater in the lane

videos.description: Kansas' Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk fouls Desmond Bane in a tie game with 2.5 seconds left to send Bane to the line to shoot 3 free throws.
videos.headline: TCU draws key foul with 2.5 seconds left

videos.description: Devonte' Graham grabs a loose ball and heaves a 3-pointer but cannot connect and Kansas is eliminated from the Big-12 tournament.
videos.headline: Graham misses 3-pointer and TCU upsets Kansas
